-- Merafe-Xstrata Venture Has Enough Ore After Government Halts Lonmin Supply
-- Alastair Reed
-- 2010-08-06T07:06:07Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-08-06/merafe-xstrata-venture-has-enough-ore-after-government-halts-lonmin-supply.html

          
          
             The chrome venture between Xstrata
Plc and Merafe Resources Ltd. has “sufficient flexibility and
adequacy of ore sources” to mitigate any short-to-medium term
impact of a government decision to stop Lonmin Plc selling
minerals other than platinum group metals.  
          
          


  


        